      "message": "Indeed! Check out this plot for some initial data: https://screenshot.googleplex.com/B5Fm2XRQXRCRH85\n\nThat just plots nsegs from the two methods with increasing conic w value (same control points always: {100, 300}, {300, 100}, {500, 300})\n\nI should double check that this data is accurate, since I threw it together pretty quickly. But it looks like the summary is there\u0027s no simple relationship, and it probably depends on the input geometry.",
